      "Multiple adaptations can affect the same parameter (e.g., explanation-depth)",
      "Adjustment methods: 'set' (absolute), 'increase' (add delta), 'decrease' (subtract delta)",
      "Adaptations only apply if profile confidence > minimumConfidence (0.6)"
    ],
    "examples": [
      {
        "profile": {
          "learningStyle": "visual",
          "pacePreference": "slow",
          "interactionStyle": "conversational"
        },
        "adaptations": [
          {
            "parameter": "example-richness",
            "value": 0.9
          },
          {
            "parameter": "analogy-usage",
            "value": 0.85
          },
          {
            "parameter": "explanation-depth",
